# The image is built from source inside the builder stage; anything generated,
# machine-local, or secret stays out so the build context is source-only and the
# result is reproducible [LAW:one-source-of-truth — one authoritative input set].
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/.data
**/dist
**/coverage
**/*.tsbuildinfo
**/test-results
**/playwright-report
.git
.github
**/.env
**/.env*.local
**/*.log
